data.body:
- VSCode Version: 1.9.1
- OS Version: OSX

Steps to Reproduce:

```javascript
  const outputChannel = window.createOutputChannel(`A channel`);
  outputChannel.show();
  setTimeout(() => {
    outputChannel.dispose()
  }, 1000);
```

The channel is left in the output channels list in the UI:

![screen shot 2017-02-16 at 6 04 22 pm](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/979966/23012522/63b80580-f472-11e6-9806-82e0b791f977.png)
